channel.description:
Well Ollie and I have been having fun Around Runescape and we've had some bad times and good times (you may of heard of Ollie in "A short Story"
We went to have a party! [img]http://img96.imageshack.us/img96/2586/intimeav2.png[/img]
I went upstairs the the bar no hot chicks =( But i Did dance! [img]http://img441.imageshack.us/img441/2292/danceqw3.png[/img]
I tryed to find Ollie! [img]http://img441.imageshack.us/img441/4848/haveyouseenolliepz3.png[/img]
I saw him on the floor drunk! [b]http://img184.imageshack.us/img184/1245/howmanydrinkskp8.png[/b]
Well while Ollie gets better in bed I thought I'd give him a break!
